    <item>
      <title>前太平洋投资管理公司 (Pimco) 和 Millennium 高管成立加密货币咨询业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/ex-pimco-millennium-executives-set-up-crypto-advisory-business</link>
      <description><![CDATA[正当业界为支持加密货币的唐纳德·特朗普再次当选美国总统而感到高兴时，千禧管理公司 (Millennium Management LLC) 和太平洋投资管理公司的前高管正在数字资产领域开展咨询业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/ex-pimco-millennium-executives-set-up-crypto-advisory-business</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 06:03:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普刺激加密货币投机活动，狗狗币价格超越比特币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/dogecoin-doge-tops-bitcoin-btc-as-trump-spurs-crypto-speculation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对当选总统唐纳德·特朗普领导下的加密货币行业前景的热情引发了一波投机热潮，最近几天，一系列小型加密货币的表现优于市场领导者比特币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/dogecoin-doge-tops-bitcoin-btc-as-trump-spurs-crypto-speculation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 05:19:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币价格突破 81,000 美元，成为特朗普时代的图腾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-10/bitcoin-btc-on-cusp-of-80-000-for-first-time-on-optimism-over-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受当选总统唐纳德·特朗普对数字资产的支持，以及国会将出现支持加密货币的立法者的前景的推动，比特币首次突破 81,000 美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-10/bitcoin-btc-on-cusp-of-80-000-for-first-time-on-optimism-over-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 10 Nov 2024 06:33:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
